sentence.text: The downstream pathways of positive regulation of cysteine-type endopeptidase activity involved in apoptotic process-Foxh1 play a critical role not only in L-R determination in the lateral plate mesoderm but also in myocardial specification and differentiation in the AHF, suggesting that TGA is a phenotype in heterotaxia as well as the primary developmental defect of the AHF.
